The '''Turkish Under 16 and Under 17 Women national basketball team''' (Turkish Young Women national basketball team), ('''{{lang-tr|YÄ±ldÄ±z Milli Basketbol TakÄ±mÄ±}}''') is the representative for [[Turkey]] in international [[basketball]] competitions, and it is organized and run by the [[Turkish Basketball Federation]]. The '''Turkish Under 16 Women national basketball team''' represents Turkey at the [[FIBA Europe Under-16 Championship for Women]] and the '''Turkish Under 17 Women national basketball team''' at the [[FIBA Under-17 World Championship for Women]].
